GP --> Svc : OK
deactivate GP

== Database ==

Svc -> DB : SELECT parent WHERE id = ?
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Parent row
deactivate DB
note right of DB : 404 if parent not found

Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO ...
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Created row
deactivate DB

Svc --> GW : 201 Created
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 201 Created
